    "description": "System Location Co.,Ltd. provides business support for finance companies in Japan and internationally. The company offers solutions for auto lease, new car sales support, and collective evaluation for present value. It also provides SYSROCKET, an ASP solution package for auto finance businesses; CA Doctor, a sales support system for new car dealers; CAV Monitor, a solution that provides calculation of the quantity of car asset value; RV Doctor, a residual value setting system; and PV Doctor, a residual value setting system. In addition, the company is involved in business solutions for automobile dealers; general planning, design, development, operation, and maintenance services for IT systems; business support for automobile finance; automotive content development business; and system service business for automobile related businesses. The company was formerly known as Dormant Company Pine Co., Ltd. and changed its name to System Location Co.,Ltd. in July 1992. System Location Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1968 and is based in Tokyo, Japan."
